{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/aws-ec2-rds","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"b7158634-bdb8-551c-9ac5-c32742c23aa2","html":"<h1 id=\"1-aws-사용법\"><a href=\"#1-aws-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"1 aws 사용법 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. AWS 사용법</h1>\n<p>EC2 실행중인 인스턴스로 가서 IPv4 퍼블릭 IP를 확인한다.\nssh를 통해 접속하는 방법은 EC2 인스턴스를 만들때 발급받은 key를 가지고 ssh로 접속한다.\n접속 방법은 다음과 같다.<br>\n<code class=\"language-text\">ssh -i my_key.pem ubuntu@IPv4</code>\n<br>나중에 개발이 끝나고 배포하게 되면 해당 아이피를 프론트 엔드 개발자에게 알려줘야 한다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"2-rds-사용법\"><a href=\"#2-rds-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"2 rds 사용법 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. RDS 사용법</h1>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 843px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2dea2619305a6fbeec607fd392e95c83/b28c0/ec2_rds.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.500593119810205%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"rds\"\n        title=\"rds\"\n        src=\"/static/2dea2619305a6fbeec607fd392e95c83/b28c0/ec2_rds.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2dea2619305a6fbeec607fd392e95c83/0783d/ec2_rds.png 240w,\n/static/2dea2619305a6fbeec607fd392e95c83/782f4/ec2_rds.png 480w,\n/static/2dea2619305a6fbeec607fd392e95c83/b28c0/ec2_rds.png 843w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 843px) 100vw, 843px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bf5f85f5a0a2c5a00bcd717d6f6eb473/76706/rds_endpoint.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 44.160997732426296%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"rds_endpoint\"\n        title=\"rds_endpoint\"\n        src=\"/static/bf5f85f5a0a2c5a00bcd717d6f6eb473/f570d/rds_endpoint.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bf5f85f5a0a2c5a00bcd717d6f6eb473/0783d/rds_endpoint.png 240w,\n/static/bf5f85f5a0a2c5a00bcd717d6f6eb473/782f4/rds_endpoint.png 480w,\n/static/bf5f85f5a0a2c5a00bcd717d6f6eb473/f570d/rds_endpoint.png 960w,\n/static/bf5f85f5a0a2c5a00bcd717d6f6eb473/8d0ff/rds_endpoint.png 1440w,\n/static/bf5f85f5a0a2c5a00bcd717d6f6eb473/76706/rds_endpoint.png 1764w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>EC2에서 RDS로 접속할때 필요하므로 RDS를 만들때 사용했던 사용자와 비밀번호는 기억해야 한다.\n위에서 확인한 엔드포인트 정보가 필요하고 접속 방법은 다음과 같다.\n<code class=\"language-text\">mysql -h [엔드포인트 주소] -u root -p</code></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/450d19b1467ec66b7d6f063a8d91ea3c/a5d5c/rds_connect.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 87.32876712328768%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"rds_connect\"\n        title=\"rds_connect\"\n        src=\"/static/450d19b1467ec66b7d6f063a8d91ea3c/f570d/rds_connect.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/450d19b1467ec66b7d6f063a8d91ea3c/0783d/rds_connect.png 240w,\n/static/450d19b1467ec66b7d6f063a8d91ea3c/782f4/rds_connect.png 480w,\n/static/450d19b1467ec66b7d6f063a8d91ea3c/f570d/rds_connect.png 960w,\n/static/450d19b1467ec66b7d6f063a8d91ea3c/8d0ff/rds_connect.png 1440w,\n/static/450d19b1467ec66b7d6f063a8d91ea3c/a5d5c/rds_connect.png 1460w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1 id=\"3-ec2에서-rds로-db-연결-확인\"><a href=\"#3-ec2%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-rds%EB%A1%9C-db-%EC%97%B0%EA%B2%B0-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"3 ec2에서 rds로 db 연결 확인 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-